"The user starts with View 1 (Overview) analyzing seasonal yields across districts through grouped bar charts. By clicking crops of interest, View 2 (Exploration) updates to show extreme performers via lollipop charts. Interactions in View 2 filter View 3's boxplots to highlight anomalies. Simultaneously, View 4 provides water efficiency insights through heatmaps. Selections propagate to View 5 showing soil-yield correlations in scatterplots. Finally, View 6 synthesizes findings via radar charts showing production clusters."